init_text: An alien has kidnapped Matt Damon, not knowing what lengths humanity goes through to retrieve him whenever he goes missing.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Once again we scramble to find out what happened to him and where he is.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He has done many great things for humanity such as his work helping to feed the hungry.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: When the team gets on board, they encounter all kinds of alien security and must use their own methods to get through.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They have to fight their way down the long hallway filled with alien soldiers and traps.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: It is a hard fought battle, but in the end they make it to Matt.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: It is the "biggest and baddest" robot they have ever encountered.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He is worth too much to humanity and the devastation that would follow his capture would be unimaginable.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The president agrees and they begin to prepare for his transport.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The team goes to see him off and wishes him luck, Matt thanks them for the help and says he will never forget them.
